%% Diagram: Optimistic Update Reconciliation
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CA as Client A
    participant MP as Multiplayer Server (Rust)
    participant CB as Client B

    Note over CA: User edits prop P on object O — set fill = red
    CA->>CA: apply locally and mark unacked
    CA->>MP: delta(O, P, red, seq 42)

    Note over CB: Concurrent edit on same prop — set fill = blue
    CB->>CB: apply locally and mark unacked
    CB->>MP: delta(O, P, blue, seq 43)

    Note over MP: Server applies in arrival order — seq 43 wins for P on O
    MP-->>CA: broadcast(O, P, blue, seq 43)
    MP-->>CB: ack(O, P, blue, seq 43)

    Note over CA: Conflict rule — discard server change for P while local P is unacked
    CA->>CA: keep red (still unacked)

    MP-->>CA: ack(O, P, red, seq 42)
    Note over MP: Server processed seq 42 after 43 — broadcast wins-loss order
    MP-->>CB: broadcast(O, P, red, seq 42)

    CA->>CA: clear unacked and finalize red
    CB->>CB: replace local and finalize red
